queries.sql: SELECT `vr`.`id`, `vr`.`group_code`, `vr`.`v_code`, `vr`.`visitor_name`, `vr`.`visitor_email`, `vr`.`visitor_phone`, `vr`.`purpose`, `vr`.`visit_date`, `vr`.`visit_time`, `vr`.`vehicle_no`, `vr`.`vehicle_type`, `vr`.`securityCheckStatus`, `vr`.`status`, `vr`.`spendTime`, `vrh`.`company`, `vrh`.`department`, `ref_by`.`name` as `reffered_by`, MAX(sgl.check_in_time) AS check_in_time, MAX(sgl.check_out_time) AS check_out_time, CASE WHEN MAX(sgl.check_out_time) IS NULL THEN 'IN' ELSE 'OUT' END AS visit_status FROM `visitors` `vr` LEFT JOIN `visitor_request_header` `vrh` ON `vrh`.`id` = `vr`.`request_header_id` LEFT JOIN `security_gate_logs` `sgl` ON `sgl`.`visitor_request_id` = `vr`.`id` LEFT JOIN `users` `ref_by` ON `ref_by`.`id` = `vrh`.`referred_by` WHERE DATE(vr.visit_date) >= '2025-12-21' AND DATE(vr.visit_date) <= '2025-12-24' AND `vr`.`status` = 'approved' GROUP BY `vr`.`id` ORDER BY `check_in_time` DESC
